<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>RouteSync | Smarter Travel for MUJ Day Scholars</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="landing-header">
    <div class="logo">RouteSync</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Smarter Travel for MUJ Day Scholars</h1>
      <p>RouteSync helps you track your rides, monitor attendance, and stay safe with real-time updates.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/login" class="btn primary">Login</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3050/3050455.png" alt="Travel" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="features" class="features">
    <h2>Why RouteSync?</h2>
    <div class="feature-cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Live Tracking</h3>
        <p>Know where your driver is and when your ride arrives.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Smart Scheduling</h3>
        <p>Automatically assign students to nearest drivers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Emergency Protocol</h3>
        <p>Send real-time alerts to the operator with one click.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="about">
    <h2>About RouteSync</h2>
    <p>RouteSync is built exclusively for Manipal University Jaipur day scholars to ease their daily travel, track attendance, and stay connected with their drivers, operators, and college authorities in a secure and efficient way.</p>
  </section>

